---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for our automated content generation website."
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 mb-8">
        <p class="text-blue-800">
          <strong>Note:</strong> This is a template privacy policy for an automated content website. 
          Consult with legal professionals to ensure compliance with applicable laws.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is primarily an automated content platform. We collect minimal personal information:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Automatically Collected Data:</strong> When you visit our site, we may collect non-personal information such as your IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URLs, and pages visited.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to analyze trends, administer the website, and gather demographic information.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our content.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the collected information for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Analyzing website traffic and user behavior</li>
        <li>Improving content quality and relevance</li>
        <li>Understanding which articles are most valuable to readers</li>
        <li>Technical maintenance and security</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For traffic analysis (see Google's privacy policy)</li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> For displaying advertisements (see Google's advertising privacy policy)</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel:</strong> For website hosting and performance monitoring</li>
        <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> For database storage (content and analytics)</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small files stored on your device. We use cookies to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Understand user preferences</li>
        <li>Track anonymous usage statistics</li>
        <li>Improve website performance</li>
        <li>Serve relevant advertisements</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect some website features.
      </p>
      
      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement reasonable security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction of data. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure.
      </p>
      
      <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
      </p>
      
      <h2>7. Automated Content Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses automated systems and artificial intelligence to generate content. 
        Articles are created by algorithms and reviewed for quality, but may contain inaccuracies.
        Always verify important information with authoritative sources.
      </p>
      
      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy periodically. The "Last updated" date at the top indicates when changes were made.
      </p>
      
      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our contact page.
      </p>
      
      <h2>10. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The right to access your personal information</li>
        <li>The right to correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>The right to request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>The right to opt-out of data collection</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise these rights, please contact us.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Important Notes</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>This website is an automated system - human review of content is limited</li>
          <li>We do not sell personal data to third parties</li>
          <li>We comply with applicable privacy laws and regulations</li>
          <li>For medical, financial, or legal advice, consult qualified professionals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>